        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued July 29 at 3:22PM MDT by NWS Glasgow MT</headline>
        <description>At 321 PM MDT, Doppler radar was tracking a strong thunderstorm near
Hillside, or 33 miles southeast of Jordan, moving east at 20 mph.

HAZARD...Nickel size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor damage to outdoor objects is possible.

Locations impacted include...
Cohagen, Hillside, and Crow Rock.
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
